query:
DELETE FROM clientes 
WHERE clienteHash IN (
  SELECT clienteHash FROM (
    SELECT clienteHash
    FROM clientes
    GROUP BY clienteHash
    HAVING COUNT(*) > 1
  ) AS dups
)
AND id NOT IN (
  SELECT max_id FROM (
    SELECT MAX(id) as max_id
    FROM clientes
    WHERE clienteHash IN (
      SELECT clienteHash FROM (
        SELECT clienteHash
        FROM clientes
        GROUP BY clienteHash
        HAVING COUNT(*) > 1
      ) AS dups2
    )
    GROUP BY clienteHash
  ) AS keep_ids
);
